creator: Pruvit Ventures, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Commit to be 1% BETTER Every Day with daily, habit-forming actions from Prüvit. Creating habits on our own can be challenging, but we're more likely to complete our goal if we commit to someone. That's why the Prüvit Every Day app helps you connect with up to 4 Accountability Partners from your Community to stay on track as a team. The more often you check in with your Accountability Team, the more likely you'll crush your goal!
Drive home your new habits with daily journal prompts each time you mark an action complete, so your Accountability Partner/s can help monitor your progress.
1% Better does not mean 'perfect'. That's why you are allotted 2 'Skips' each week without affecting your Streak. Be committed to increasing your Operating Level by igniting a daily action winning streak, and participate in monthly challenges and rewards.
Stop thinking, START DOING, and Prüvit Every Day.
